{"tid":255274,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"人生第一次叫雞經歷","createTime":"2017-05-23T20:01:56.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-23T20:35:50.000Z","uid":111748,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"a9a4660413d9335e1d285fefa037796d5a0a637b","tid":255274,"uid":111748,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-23T20:01:56.000Z","msg":"同女朋友分左手之後，就開始日日打飛機，過左幾個月，直到今日，終於忍唔住要去叫雞。<br />\n㩒完鐘問完價，見到馬來西亞有波有樣有腳諗住實冇死，即刻衝入房，入到房見到佢仲wechat緊，咁算啦，自己除衫自己沖涼，沖完涼出到嚟，見到佢已經瞓左喺到，叫我上床。<br />\n撩佢嘅時候仲wechat緊，要我自己帶套都算啦，屌極都係粒聲唔出，人生第一次叫雞就屌<span style=\"font-size: large;\">死魚</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 咁就緊係乜癮都冇哂，諗住kiss變返硬啲，佢竟然話唔俾kiss<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我已經冇哂希望，諗住快啲射完快啲走，屌到就射嘅時候，佢無端端拎部電話出嚟<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">Facetime</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 話哂我都屌緊佢，可唔可以俾啲尊重我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我灰到變返做半硬，諗住叫佢幫我bj，佢話No，最後就以hj結束人生第一次叫雞之旅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 走嘅時候都係我自己一個沖涼<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n不滿:<br />\n1.唔俾kiss<br />\n2.死魚<br />\n3.Facetime<br />\n經過今次經歷之後，<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">我發誓以後唔叫雞！！！</span></span>"},{"pid":"f3cd40080630f8d9b9b8e6e75b7d24403a0368fc","tid":255274,"uid":42097,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-23T20:04:01.000Z","msg":"巴打去邊樹玩<br />\n咩價位<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2e2186b9897ec19061679ac45ad3146c2289447e","tid":255274,"uid":4517,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-23T20:09:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6b7392e9108fd8cde30d573fa33396f2ec94a283","tid":255274,"uid":111748,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,